com.interpss.core.algo.config

Interface LfAdjustAccFactor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LfAdjustAccFactorImpl

    public interface LfAdjustAccFactor
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Lf Adjust Acc Factor'. Loadflow bus/branch adjustment/control acceleration facotor configuration class

    The following features are supported:

    • Pv Limit Acc Factor
    • Pq Limit Acc Factor
    • Re QBus Acc Factor
    • Svc Adjust Acc Factor
    • Xfr Tap Control Acc Factor
    • Ps Xfr PControl Acc Factor
    See Also:
    LfAdjAlgoConfigPackage.getLfAdjustAccFactor()
